information it published he said 
prodigy may not have as great a duty wright said that would 
depend on whether a judge or jury found it to be more like a 
newspaper or magazine which have a greater duty to monitor content 
than entities not in that business 
where they would stand in terms of liability is unclear he 
said there are few if any statutes or lawsuits as precedent 
