exonerated the nazi murderers but turned them into messengers of 
god who were sent to punish the people of israel for not observing 
the torah 
but another caller an ultraorthodox woman who lost relatives 
in the holocaust defended the rabbi 
with al the pain i have i can understand his words we 
believe in the link between sin and punishment said the woman 
who did not give her name 
