barrys legal travails as a national tragedy but insisted that 
the mayor should be remembered for his wide range of 
accomplishments particularly the development of a minority 
contracting procedure that generates more than 600 million 
annually for businesses owned by africanamericans hispanics and 
other groups 
on that front marion barry took the city to a new level and 
that was a great example to other municipalities stallings said 
he was a very strong leader and that should not be forgotten 
either 
barry was both relaxed and reflective as he prepared to leave 
the job he has held for a dozen years but he demonstrated none of 
