the interregional group of deputies which represents 229 
deputies in the congress of peoples deputies showed reporters 
what they said were seven ballots that were not submitted for 
tabulation at the thursday session that elected yanayev tass 
reported 
parliament officials charged with counting the votes had 
reported that only five ballots were not put into ballot boxes 
