postponement saying urgently needed reforms and constitutional 
changes require that parliamentary elections as soon as possible 
alia on wednesday acknowledged there have been mistakes in 
the 46 years of oneparty rule he pledged to reform the communist 
party and remove the communists guaranteed leading role in society 
from the constitution 
he also promised reforms to shore up albanias isolationist 
economy now on the brink of collapse 
