call in sick on a given day but since dec 21 more than 500 a day 
have been out sick some 250 pilots are over in saudi arabia for 
operation desert shield and that compounds the problem she added 
the temporary restraining order came late wednesday from us 
district judge john mcbryde barring pilots from actions designed to 
influence contract negotiations 
the union said it will challenge the ruling which it called a 
rush to judgment 
